outputs.output_descr:
Outputs:
1. An enabling policy frame work to support an effective system for the environment management and ecosystem conservation established.
2. Governance Community (men, women and youth ) participation in democratic processes and structures at District level enhanced
3. Sustainable Growth & Social Protection Improved and sustainable productivity and income generation for all community members
4. Health/Nutr/WASH & Population Control Health status of the resettled population improved and the population growth reduced within the settlement
5. children are enrolled, stay in school and complete a full cycle of basic education
6 HIV Resettled populations adopt protective behaviors and use quality HIV prevention, treatment, care and support services

project_descr: Mutobo Integrated Sustainable  Development Songhai Model Project
